# Supabase Configuration
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url_here
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace the values with your actual Supabase project URL and anon key
# 3. You can find these values in your Supabase project settings > API
# 4. The .env.local file will be ignored by git for security